{"data":[{"date":"16:03 24/07","title":"Leroy Sane: \u201cCh\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc Man City\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/leroy-sane-danh-gia-cao-chelsea-o-mua-giai-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Leroy Sane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Conte, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Maurizio Sarri. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Jorginho t\u1eeb Napoli.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leroy Sane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Leroy Sane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Leroy-Sane-phat-bieu-ve-Chelsea-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi th\u00eam 140 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam 3 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus, bao g\u1ed3m: Trung v\u1ec7 Rugani, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Higuain v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pjanic.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u01b0ng \u00fd nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sane \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leroy Sane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leroy Sane phat bieu ve Chelsea\" title=\"Leroy Sane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/leroy-sane-danh-gia-cao-chelsea-o-mua-giai-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leroy Sane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1ch Napoli ch\u01a1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. Man City \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ecd \u1edf Champions League v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV Sarri s\u1ebd \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t HLV th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1eefa trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u1ecd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Perth Glory v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0 v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Pedro. \u1ede tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/perth-glory-vs-chelsea-tran-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191830.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea 1-0 Perth Glory</span>, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 cho ra m\u1eaft t\u00e2n binh Jorginho, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1585","checkdouble":"191919"},{"date":"16:24 24/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/vidal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Arturo Vidal th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Bayern Munich trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arturo Vidal \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n r\u1eddi Bayern Munich</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch 25 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e8 2018, trong danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arturo Vidal kh\u00f4ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Vidal \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n r\u1eddi \"H\u00f9m x\u00e1m\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua Arturo Vidal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mua Arturo Vidal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/10/MU-mua-Arturo-Vidal-voi-gia-26-trieu-bang-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Vidal s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Bayern Munich</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Chile El Mercurio, Vidal \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Bayern Munich \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Fernando Felicevich c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Vidal mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bayern \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Leon Goretzka t\u1eeb Schalke v\u00e0 g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Renato Sanches, t\u00e2n HLV Niko\u00a0Kovac s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Vidal n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Bayern y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile s\u1ebd ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c r\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Vidal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Vidal, M.U l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ecf ra quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t. Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e1u l\u1eeda c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU co kha nang rat lon chieu mo thanh cong Vidal\" title=\"MU c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Vidal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/vidal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Vidal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Arturo Vidal th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Theo Daily Mail, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/hlv-mourinho-muon-xin-them-kinh-phi-de-nang-cap-2-vi-tri-172-191893.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mourinho mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p th\u00eam 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span> \u0111\u1ec3 mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Bayern \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi. Ngo\u00e0i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf th\u00ec Inter Milan c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i, song \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Alexis Sanchez \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho M.U, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi Old Trafford. Vidal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Mourinho. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Man \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1584","checkdouble":"191920"},{"date":"16:04 24/07","title":"Mahrez ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tham v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/mahrez-tiet-lo-tham-vong-lon-sau-khi-gia-nhap-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>San Jose Earthquakes hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng khu v\u1ef1c mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i MLS. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Man United s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5. Nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd may m\u1eafn l\u1eafm m\u1edbi c\u00f3 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf sau tr\u1eadn MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf sau tr\u1eadn MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/170116-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Man United kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. Man United t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 571 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 85%. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Mourinho tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t ch\u1eadm, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Martial, Sanchez v\u00e0 Chong tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian khi nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, qu\u00e3ng chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp gi\u1eefa h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhanh nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n. B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd, Mourinho v\u1eabn c\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Valencia \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man United. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc n\u00e0y, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ed1i t\u0103m l\u00e0 Matteo Darmian. N\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef bi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a MU l\u00e0 Fosu-Mensah, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tri\u1ec3n khai t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/video-tong-hop-mu-00-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-326-191811.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc San Jose Earthquakes</span> ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nan gi\u1ea3i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man United l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Pogba th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m sau.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1t khi thi\u1ebfu Lukaku\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba va Lukaku\" title=\"Pogba v\u00e0 Lukaku\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Nhan-dinh-co-hoi-MU-vo-dich-giai-Ngoai-hang-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>MU ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 Lukaku</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ghi b\u00e0n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Man United trong su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Ngo\u00e0i Lukaku, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tay s\u0103n b\u00e0n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m. V\u1eady n\u00ean m\u1ed7i khi thi\u1ebfu ng\u00f4i sao cao to ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester l\u1ea1i b\u1ebf t\u1eafc t\u1ed9t c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh. Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlexis Sanchez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng gi\u00fap MU thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n sau khi gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft xong c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 visa \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn M\u1ef9. V\u00e0 anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1m \u1ed5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i MLS. Nh\u01b0ng ngo\u00e0i m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, Sanchez h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMan United nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Lukaku \u1edf tour du \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 HLV Mourinho th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee9ng ra \u0111\u1ea3m tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n. C\u00e1c k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch d\u00e0i h\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i Lukaku, Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai m\u01a1 h\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Martial\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anthony Martial\" title=\"Anthony Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Wayne-Rooney-khuyen-MU-giu-chan-Martial-bang-moi-gia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Anthony Martial kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a khi \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi Martial nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00ec Man United. \u0110\u1ea7u \u00f3c c\u1ee7a Martial \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i kh\u00e1c sau khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford. V\u00e0 Mourinho c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n khi b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed Martial \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh khi quay l\u01b0ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y th\u00ec kh\u1ecfi ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Martial, Mourinho bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Martial c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Martial l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c n\u00ean l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Man United. B\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Sanchez kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Martial c\u0169ng g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p x\u1ea5u t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-arturo-vidal-sap-ky-hop-dong-voi-mu-172-191920.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ngay-hom-nay-247-187-191902.html\">Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 24/7: M.U ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua trung v\u1ec7 Maguire</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1583","checkdouble":"191921"},{"date":"16:19 24/07","title":"C\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed9c thi vi\u1ebft \"\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng World Cup 2018\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/cong-bo-ket-qua-cuoc-thi-viet-an-tuong-world-cup-2018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c cu\u1ed9c thi vi\u1ebft \"\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng World Cup 2018\" d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 trang Bongda24h.vn \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u1edbi ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Nga, BBT ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng chuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1t gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng.</h2><p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/KQ-WC18-600.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nV\u1eady l\u00e0, World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u01b0 v\u1ecb kh\u00f3 qu\u00ean cho c\u00e1c fan  h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9c  gi\u1ea3 trang Bongda24h.vn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 do th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, t\u00ecnh y\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi World  Cup n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao vua n\u00f3i chung, BBT Bongda24h.vn \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c cu\u1ed9c  thi vi\u1ebft &quot;\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng World Cup 2018&quot;. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft,  trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt b\u00e0i ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00e1ng t\u00e1c b\u1edfi c\u00e1c tay vi\u1ebft b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1  chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau th\u1eddi gian r\u00e0 so\u00e1t v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5m k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 14 b\u00e0i xu\u1ea5t  s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 trao th\u01b0\u1edfng. Danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>GI\u1ea2I NH\u1ea4T (5 tri\u1ec7u VN\u0110)<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\nWorld Cup v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/world-cup-va-nhung-bat-ngo-471-191342.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/world-cup-va-nhung-bat-ngo-471-191342.html</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>GI\u1ea2I NH\u00cc (2 tri\u1ec7u VN\u0110/gi\u1ea3i)<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n1. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t &ldquo;s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng&rdquo; ngay t\u1ea1i b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/co-mot-san-van-dong-ngay-tai-benh-vien-471-191476.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/co-mot-san-van-dong-ngay-tai-benh-vien-471-191476.html</span><br>\r\n2. Th\u01b0 g\u1eedi Neymar - C\u1eadu h\u00e3y tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n!<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/thu-gui-neymar-cau-hay-truong-thanh-hon-471-190724.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/thu-gui-neymar-cau-hay-truong-thanh-hon-471-190724.html</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>GI\u1ea2I BA (1 tri\u1ec7u VN\u0110/gi\u1ea3i)<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n1. Ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean, B\u1ed3 \u01a1i<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/tien-len-bo-oi-471-190447.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/tien-len-bo-oi-471-190447.html</span><br>\r\n2. Sinh nh\u1eadt Messi, Ronaldo g\u1eedi th\u01b0 nh\u1eafn nh\u1ee7<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/sinh-nhat-messi-ronaldo-gui-thu-nhan-nhucau-chi-la-doi-thu-thu-hai-471-189497.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/sinh-nhat-messi-ronaldo-gui-thu-nhan-nhucau-chi-la-doi-thu-thu-hai-471-189497.html</span><br>\r\n3. C\u01a1n m\u01b0a g\u1ea1ch, \u0111\u00e1&rdquo; tr\u00ean m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 c\u1ea5p b\u1ed1n!<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/con-mua-gach-da-tren-mai-nha-cap-bon-471-190194.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/con-mua-gach-da-tren-mai-nha-cap-bon-471-190194.html</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>GI\u1ea2I KHUY\u1ebeN KH\u00cdCH (500.000 VN\u0110/gi\u1ea3i)<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n1. Lionel Messi, sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, m\u00e0u anh ch\u1ecdn v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u00e0u d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/bai-du-thi-wc-lionel-messi-sau-tat-ca-mau-anh-chon-van-la-mau-dan-toc-471-191125.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/bai-du-thi-wc-lionel-messi-sau-tat-ca-mau-anh-chon-van-la-mau-dan-toc-471-191125.html</span><br>\r\n2. B\u00e0i h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng tr\u00f2n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/bai-hoc-tu-trai-bong-tron-471-191032.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/bai-hoc-tu-trai-bong-tron-471-191032.html</span><br>\r\n3. Nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa l\u00ean, h\u1ee1i nh\u1eefng v\u0169 c\u00f4ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i!<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/bai-du-thi-nhay-mua-len-hoi-nhung-vu-cong-huyen-thoai-471-189035.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/bai-du-thi-nhay-mua-len-hoi-nhung-vu-cong-huyen-thoai-471-189035.html</span><br>\r\n4. T\u00f4i nh\u1edb Anh - Edison Cavani<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/toi-nho-anh-471-190929.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/toi-nho-anh-471-190929.html</span><br>\r\n5. Th\u00e2n g\u1eedi Messi, th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i!<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/than-gui-messi-than-tuong-cua-toi-471-189483.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/than-gui-messi-than-tuong-cua-toi-471-189483.html</span><br>\r\n6. Th\u01a1 t\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/tho-tong-ket-world-cup-2018-471-191589.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/tho-tong-ket-world-cup-2018-471-191589.html</span><br>\r\n7. Th\u01b0 g\u1eedi Kasper: Cha t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 con!<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/thu-gui-kasper-cha-tu-hao-ve-con-471-190335.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/thu-gui-kasper-cha-tu-hao-ve-con-471-190335.html</span><br>\r\n8. Croatia - \u0110\u00e2u \u0111\u00f3 b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam <br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/croatia-dau-do-bong-dang-u23-viet-nam-471-191366.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://bongda24h.vn/an-tuong-world-cup/croatia-dau-do-bong-dang-u23-viet-nam-471-191366.html</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c thi nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ec7 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, trong v\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 n\u00e0o ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft trong danh s\u00e1ch tr\u00fang gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u1ec7t k\u00ea ph\u00eda tr\u00ean vi ph\u1ea1m th\u1ec3 l\u1ec7 (nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 hay sao ch\u00e9p, x\u00e0o n\u1ea5u c\u00e1c b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c) th\u00ec vui l\u00f2ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o l\u1ea1i cho BTC qua \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 email <strong>gocbandoc@bongda24h.vn</strong>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi x\u00e1c minh n\u1ebfu l\u1eddi khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i trao gi\u1ea3i cho c\u00e1c b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft vi ph\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 kh\u00e1c x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng h\u01a1n. Sau m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i n\u00e0o, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh trao gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXin tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tham gia t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 Bongda24h.vn cho cu\u1ed9c thi vi\u1ebft &quot;\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng World Cup 2018&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1582","checkdouble":"191922"},{"date":"16:52 24/07","title":"3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \"gi\u00e1 m\u1ec1m\" m\u00e0 Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 thay v\u00ec Eden Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/3-muc-tieu-gia-mem-ma-real-madrid-co-the-chieu-mo-thay-vi-eden-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi chia tay Ronaldo, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Hazard nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 CR7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00ean t\u1edbi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro. V\u00e0 d\u0129 nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn 'gi\u00e1 m\u1ec1m' h\u01a1n cho Real.</h2><h2>3. Anthony Martial</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martial kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed3i cho Real trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Mourinho song Martial v\u1eabn k\u1ecbp ghi nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi 31 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 131 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Martial song v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1 \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00ednh c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf Wayne Rooney, Martial l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League, n\u1ebfu anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1ed1t. M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Martial l\u00e0 Ander Herrera c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng anh th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 thay v\u00ec Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 thay v\u00ec Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/3-muc-tieu-ma-Real-Madrid-co-the-chieu-mo-thay-vi-Eden-Hazard-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Martial s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn '\u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ec1n' v\u1edbi CLB Real Madrid</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Martial v\u1edbi M.U s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m sau tuy nhi\u00ean hai b\u00ean v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Do v\u1eady \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 Real nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u00e9p gi\u00e1 Man United.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN th\u00ec c\u1ea3 Chelsea, Tottenham v\u00e0 Bayern Munich \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Martial nh\u01b0ng HLV Mourinho ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n anh cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Real Madrid. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Martial m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 22 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.</p>\r\n<h2>2. Sadio Mane</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m c\u1ea1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Mohamed Salah, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sadio Mane c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool. V\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9, Mane lu\u00f4n cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng The Kop/\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 20 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Liverpool tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1edd t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Mane lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Real ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, HLV Zidane \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverpool nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac khi c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean Mane v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u00edch h\u1ee3p tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Real. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Mane ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 d\u01b0\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/chuyen-nhuong-c187-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span> th\u00edch h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n Hazard \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah va Mane\" title=\"Salah va Mane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/liverpool-toi-my-du-dau-tam-tau-ke-o-nguoi-di.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 Mane r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi Real</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>1. Ivan Perisic</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Croatia l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup. V\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1nh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, Perisic lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c th\u1eeba. Trong vai tr\u00f2 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng pha \u0111i b\u00f3ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c x\u00e9 toang h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ivan Perisic la tru cot cua Inter\" title=\"Ivan Perisic la tru cot cua Inter\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Ivan-Perisic-la-tru-cot-cua-Inter.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ivan Perisic \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i\u00a0Real Madrid</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i, m\u1ed7i khi x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp trung l\u1ed9, Perisic th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, ho\u1eb7c t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o \u1edf nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00e1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, khi anh lu\u00f4n l\u00f9i s\u00e2u tranh ch\u1ea5p khu gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Perisic ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 50 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t 'm\u00f3n h\u1eddi' cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y thay v\u00ec c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng s\u1edf h\u1eefu Eden Hazard t\u1eeb Chelsea.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2407-180-191907.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2407.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2407-180-191907.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 24/07</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 24/07.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-no-luc-chieu-mo-sat-thu-serie-a-180-191701.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/22/real-no-luc-chieu-mo-sat-thu-serie-a.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-no-luc-chieu-mo-sat-thu-serie-a-180-191701.html\">Real mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201cs\u00e1t th\u1ee7\u201d Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Marca, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, Mauro Icardi \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ronaldo-ra-di-ai-se-mang-ve-50-ban-thang-moi-mua-cho-real-187-191545.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-he-2018-hua-hen-se-no-bom-tan-sau-CR7-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ronaldo-ra-di-ai-se-mang-ve-50-ban-thang-moi-mua-cho-real-187-191545.html\">Ronaldo ra \u0111i: Ai s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a cho Real?</span><br>\r\nChia tay Cristiano Ronaldo, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n \u0111i m\u1ed9t c\u00e2y s\u0103n b\u00e0n c\u1ef1 ph\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u00e2u ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1581","checkdouble":"191925"},{"date":"17:08 24/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a MU sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a nh\u1ea1t San Jose Earthquakes","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/nhung-van-de-cua-mu-sau-tran-hoa-nhat-san-jose-earthquakes.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>San Jose Earthquakes hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng khu v\u1ef1c mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i MLS. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Man United s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5. Nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd may m\u1eafn l\u1eafm m\u1edbi c\u00f3 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf sau tr\u1eadn MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf sau tr\u1eadn MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/170116-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Man United kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. Man United t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 571 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 85%. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Mourinho tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t ch\u1eadm, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Martial, Sanchez v\u00e0 Chong tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian khi nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, qu\u00e3ng chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp gi\u1eefa h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhanh nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n. B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd, Mourinho v\u1eabn c\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Valencia \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man United. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc n\u00e0y, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ed1i t\u0103m l\u00e0 Matteo Darmian. N\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef bi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a MU l\u00e0 Fosu-Mensah, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tri\u1ec3n khai t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/video-tong-hop-mu-00-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-326-191811.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc San Jose Earthquakes</span> ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nan gi\u1ea3i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man United l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Pogba th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m sau.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1t khi thi\u1ebfu Lukaku\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba va Lukaku\" title=\"Pogba v\u00e0 Lukaku\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Nhan-dinh-co-hoi-MU-vo-dich-giai-Ngoai-hang-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>MU ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 Lukaku</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ghi b\u00e0n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Man United trong su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Ngo\u00e0i Lukaku, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tay s\u0103n b\u00e0n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m. V\u1eady n\u00ean m\u1ed7i khi thi\u1ebfu ng\u00f4i sao cao to ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester l\u1ea1i b\u1ebf t\u1eafc t\u1ed9t c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh. Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlexis Sanchez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng gi\u00fap MU thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n sau khi gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft xong c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 visa \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn M\u1ef9. V\u00e0 anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1m \u1ed5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i MLS. Nh\u01b0ng ngo\u00e0i m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, Sanchez h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMan United nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Lukaku \u1edf tour du \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 HLV Mourinho th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee9ng ra \u0111\u1ea3m tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n. C\u00e1c k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch d\u00e0i h\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i Lukaku, Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai m\u01a1 h\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Martial\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anthony Martial\" title=\"Anthony Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Wayne-Rooney-khuyen-MU-giu-chan-Martial-bang-moi-gia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Anthony Martial kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a khi \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi Martial nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00ec Man United. \u0110\u1ea7u \u00f3c c\u1ee7a Martial \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i kh\u00e1c sau khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford. V\u00e0 Mourinho c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n khi b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed Martial \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh khi quay l\u01b0ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y th\u00ec kh\u1ecfi ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Martial, Mourinho bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Martial c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Martial l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c n\u00ean l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Man United. B\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Sanchez kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Martial c\u0169ng g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p x\u1ea5u t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-arturo-vidal-sap-ky-hop-dong-voi-mu-172-191920.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ngay-hom-nay-247-187-191902.html\">Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 24/7: M.U ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua trung v\u1ec7 Maguire</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1580","checkdouble":"191926"},{"date":"17:48 24/07","title":"Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia l\u00ean 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/7/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-trung-ve-nguoi-italia-len-45-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rugani</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/Chelsea-mua-Daniele-Rugani-voi-gia-45-trieu-bang-tu-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Juventus 2 l\u1ea7n t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Rugani cho Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Napoli t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Rugani ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n 20 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Serie A, anh g\u1eb7p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea tin r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho Rugani kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt g\u1eb7p ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf Milan, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong vi\u1ec7c th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Juventus. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb, Chelsea sau \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia l\u00ean 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 h\u1ecfi mua Rugani</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-sap-cong-bo-tan-binh-thu-2-tri-gia-36-trieu-bang-172-191548.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia. The Blues \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rugani nhieu kha nang se tro thanh tan binh dau tien cua Arsenal o He 2018\" title=\"Rugani nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/chelsea-sap-cong-bo-tan-binh-thu-2-tri-gia-36-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Rugani l\u00ean 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y kinh ph\u00ed chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea3 David Luiz v\u00e0 Gary Cahill. The Blues d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh s\u1ebd thu v\u1ec1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Rugani n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 HLV Sarri: \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y, Sarri l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV t\u1ed1t. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u01a1n \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa Rugani v\u1edbi Juventus v\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn 3 n\u0103m, ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u01b0ng v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Chelsea. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Juventus c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng hay kh\u00f4ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1579","checkdouble":"191927"},{"date":"17:29 24/07","title":"Scholes l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mourinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/scholes-chi-trich-mourinho-vi-da-giao-huu-qua-kem.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Paul Scholes r\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 Man United v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 HLV Jose Mourinho sau 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf M\u1ef9 h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>MU \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch v\u1edbi 19 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u00edt h\u01a1n nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Man City t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. V\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tour du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 b\u1eb1ng hai m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Club America v\u00e0 San Jose Earthquakes.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Fred v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap cho NHM c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Man City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb san l\u1ea5p. Nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng HLV Mourinho v\u1eabn mong mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Scholes ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mourinho v\u00ec qu\u00e1 coi tr\u1ecdng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Scholes ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mourinho v\u00ec qu\u00e1 coi tr\u1ecdng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/scholes-chi-trich-mourinho-vi-da-giao-huu-qua-kem.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Scholes ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mourinho v\u00ec qu\u00e1 coi tr\u1ecdng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Paul Scholes v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong th\u1eddi gian qua.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cMourinho c\u00f3 l\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Man United thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo phong c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y mong mu\u1ed1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ea1o ra k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t thay v\u00ec l\u00e0m cho b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Mourinho h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t trong su\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng n\u0103m c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu Pep Guardiola l\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a Man United, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t gh\u00e9t nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Mourinho l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 d\u1ef1a theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Tr\u1eafng tay th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi MU</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Man United \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o. V\u00e0 Scholes tin r\u1eb1ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cN\u0103m ngo\u00e1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Man United kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1edfi Sevilla, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 \u1edf Champions League. \u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft FA Cup nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed7i n\u0103m tr\u1eafng tay \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi Man United\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-van-de-cua-mu-sau-tran-hoa-nhat-san-jose-earthquakes-172-191926.html\">Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a MU sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a nh\u1ea1t San Jose Earthquakes</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-cau-thu-vo-danh-172-191899.html\">MU chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 danh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1578","checkdouble":"191929"},{"date":"17:19 24/07","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Willian t\u1edbi Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-willian-toi-barca.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Willian t\u1edbi Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Pedro</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, HLV Conte th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Willian v\u00e0 Pedro \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 17 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00e0 20 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Willian t\u1edbi Barca  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Willian t\u1edbi Barca  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-Willian-toi-Barca--hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pedro h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i n\u1ebfu Willian ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Willian l\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Pedro. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 c\u00f3 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Barca ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 4 b\u00e0n c\u00f9ng 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Napoli, HLV Maurizio Sarri th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea \u00f4ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Willian s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u01a1n Pedro \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu Willian t\u1edbi Barca, nghi\u1ec5m nhi\u00ean Pedro s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Camp Nou, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi vui nh\u1ea5t, b\u1edfi c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eden Hazard \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Los Blancos, anh c\u0169ng b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri muon bien Hazard thanh trung tam trong loi choi cua Chelsea\" title=\"Sarri mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/muon-thanh-cong-hlv-sarri-can-phai-ban-eden-hazard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1ebd gi\u1eef Hazard n\u1ebfu m\u1ea5t Willian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191665.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Eden Hazard</span>, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu Willian c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Hazard s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid. HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu m\u1ea5t Willian \u00f4ng s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c gi\u1eef Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Philippe Coutinho</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Philippe Coutinho l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Willian nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ef1u sao Liverpool mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u01b0a b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Camp Nou.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Coutinho se rat vui neu Willian toi Barca\" title=\"Coutinho s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t vui n\u1ebfu Willian t\u1edbi Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/coutinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Coutinho s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t vui n\u1ebfu Willian t\u1edbi Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Sport, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Coutinho thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c HLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng khi\u1ebfn Coutinho h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, Barca 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua Willian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 50, 53 v\u00e0 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCoutinho ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi vui nh\u1ea5t n\u1ebfu Barca \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Willian. Hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nhau 30 l\u1ea7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Brazil, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 5 l\u1ea7n \u1edf World Cup 2018.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 am hi\u1ec3u gi\u1eefa Coutinho v\u00e0 Willian s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Barca c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Coutinho c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Willian h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Ousmane Dembele</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ousmane Dembele c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 105 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh ch\u1ec9 ghi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 19 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf La Liga. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Dembele th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ousmane Dembele co the roi Camp Nou neu Barca mua Willian\" title=\"Ousmane Dembele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Camp Nou n\u1ebfu Barca mua Willian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/dem.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ousmane Dembele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Camp Nou n\u1ebfu Barca mua Willian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Willian, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ousmane Dembele ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. V\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t, Willian ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3, Willian s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Messi v\u00e0 Suarez l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Dembele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Barca ngay \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Wilfried Zaha</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian, HLV Sarri s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n duy nh\u1ea5t Pedro l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wilfried Zaha co co hoi khoac ao Chelsea neu Willian ra di\" title=\"Wilfried Zaha c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea n\u1ebfu Willian ra \u0111i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/zaha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wilfried Zaha c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea n\u1ebfu Willian ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAnthony Martial l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, song Mourinho \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf l\u1ea1i. M.U d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n t\u1ef1 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eafn ch\u1eb7t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Martial t\u1ea1i Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo ESPN v\u00e0 Mirror, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Wilfried Zaha c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 cao trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, anh c\u00f3 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nZaha \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Palace, anh \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. N\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Chelsea, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ef1u sao M.U s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1edbi Stamford Bridge, Zaha s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 MU</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Willian, qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf Chelsea gi\u00fap \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988. Mourinho c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho rat muon tai hop voi Willian o MU\" title=\"Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Willian \u1edf MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/mou.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Willian \u1edf MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 55 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Willian \u1edf Old Trafford, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c M.U chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i. Daily Mail v\u00e0 Goal \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu Willian c\u1ee7a MU v\u00e0 Mourinho tan th\u00e0nh m\u00e2y kh\u00f3i. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, Chelsea s\u1ebd \u01b0u ti\u00ean b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca thay v\u00ec M.U, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 sai l\u1ea7m khi b\u00e1n Matic cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1577","checkdouble":"191930"},{"date":"17:54 24/07","title":"C\u1ef1u sao NHA c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u00e2n HLV Chelsea m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u nguy hi\u1ec3m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/20/di-canio-canh-bao-sarri-ve-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Di Canio c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Sarri. Theo c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, v\u1ecb HLV \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Italia c\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh l\u1ea1i th\u00f3i quen l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 ng\u00f4i sao Eden Hazard nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Hazard</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEden Hazard m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i thi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap \u0110T B\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau World Cup, Hazard b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea. Sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, anh chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. Real Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng 3 l\u1ea7n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Cristiano Ronaldo hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Di Canio c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Sarri v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Di Canio c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Sarri v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/Di-Canio-canh-bao-Sarri-ve-Eden-Hazard-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hazard t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-canh-bao-real-madrid-vu-eden-hazard-172-191840.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real Madrid v\u1ee5 Eden Hazard</span>. H\u1ecd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Lille tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n t\u1eeb g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110i\u1ec1u Sarri c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHazard v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Huddersfield v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 11 th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi. Paolo Di Canio, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Sheffield Wednesday, West Ham v\u00e0 Charlton Athletic lo ng\u1ea1i phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi Hazard.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard\" title=\"Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/di-canio-canh-bao-sarri-ve-hazard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Di Canio c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Sarri v\u1ec1 Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u Sarri c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang t\u1edbi Chelsea \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo;, Di Canio c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Sarri. &ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n xem l\u1ea1i c\u00e1ch qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3ng khung trong m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 Hazard ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 do tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Sarri ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c Sarri c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u01b0u t\u00e2m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Sarri. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Perth Glory trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i Australia nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Pedro Rodriguez chi\u1ec1u h\u00f4m qua (23/7). \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Hazard c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u1ee7a Chelsea kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 v\u00ec c\u00f2n \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ph\u00e9p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-trung-ve-nguoi-italia-len-45-trieu-bang-172-191927.html\">Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia l\u00ean 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chot-gia-ban-willian-cho-barca-172-191898.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sarri-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-cho-chelsea-he-nay-172-191875.html\">Sarri \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Chelsea h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/mbappe-xui-giuc-kante-bo-chelsea-sang-psg-184-191870.html\">Mbappe x\u00fai gi\u1ee5c Kante b\u1ecf Chelsea sang PSG</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ra-mat-suon-se-tan-hlv-chelsea-duoc-so-sanh-voi-pep-guardiola-172-191856.html\">Ra m\u1eaft su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, t\u00e2n HLV Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Pep Guardiola</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1576","checkdouble":"191934"},{"date":"09:49 24/07","title":"Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Liverpool lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/liverpool-don-tin-du-tu-hang-thu-matip-chan-thuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Joel Matip \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chia tay gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu ICC \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 trung t\u00e2m t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Dortmund.</h2><h2>Matip g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Joel Matip \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb thay ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n ngay trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-13-dortmund-icc-2018-329-191807.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Liverpool v\u00e0 Dortmund</span> cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua. HLV Jurgen Klopp lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 b\u1eafp \u0111\u00f9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ebft \u0111au kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf c\u01a1 kh\u00e1c. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u01a1 b\u1eafp. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ebft r\u00e1ch nh\u1ecf\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Klopp l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Matip\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Liverpool lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Liverpool lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/liverpool-don-tin-du-tu-hang-thu-matip-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Klopp t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Cameroon m\u1edbi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Dortmund, Klopp v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cJoel Matip s\u1ebd r\u1eddi tr\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Liverpool t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u01a1 m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Dortmund h\u00f4m Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 gi\u1eefa hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng n\u1eb1m \u1edf g\u1ea7n ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f9i m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 n\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u. D\u1eabu sao, Matip c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Merseyside v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i Melwood\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Matip, Liverpool s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Van Dijk \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 Joe Gomez v\u00e0 Ragnar Klavan. C\u1ea3 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t s\u1edbm m\u1ed9t chi\u1ec1u. V\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf, The Kop \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 ph\u00e1 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-danh-sach-7-cau-thu-giup-liverpool-thu-ve-100-trieu-bang-172-191890.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Danh s\u00e1ch 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap Liverpool thu v\u1ec1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-liverpool-dung-ky-vong-qua-nhieu-vao-alisson-172-191888.html\">NHM Liverpool \u0111\u1eebng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Alisson</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1575","checkdouble":"191895"},{"date":"09:51 24/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PAOK vs Basel 0h30 ng\u00e0y 25/7 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/nhan-dinh-paok-vs-basel-0h30-ngay-257-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PAOK vs Basel l\u00fac 0h30 ng\u00e0y 25/7 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19)): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PAOK vs Basel 0h30 ng\u00e0y 257 Champions League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PAOK vs Basel 0h30 ng\u00e0y 257 Champions League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/PAOK-vs-Basel.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">PAOK vs Basel</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>PAOK vs Basel: 2-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, PAOK c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG\u00a0Hy L\u1ea1p. V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y, PAOK gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 Champions League t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Basel, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng 20 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch 8 m\u00f9a v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp khi c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 chung cu\u1ed9c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Young Boys t\u1edbi 15 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 sa s\u00fat tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Basel.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Basel ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 th\u1ee5t l\u00f9i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Basel to\u00e0n thua 4 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2018/19. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, tr\u1eadn thua t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 St. Gallen, ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi Hy L\u1ea1p n\u00e0y, Basel ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 tr\u1eafng tay, b\u1edfi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1edb h\u00eanh v\u1edbi 13 b\u00e0n thua \u1edf 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, d\u00f9 Basel kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n, b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y, PAOK nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nPAOK: P. Glykos, L\u00e9o Matos, S. Malezas, D. Chatziisaias, S. Kitsiou, Maur\u00edcio -O. El Kaddouri, G. Ktistopoulos, D. Limnios, G. Vrakas, I. Mystakidis.<br>\r\nBasel: J. Omlin, M. Such\u00fd, S. Widmer, \u00c9. \u00c1lvarez, E. C\u00fcmart, S. Di\u00e9, Z. Kuzmanovi\u0107, T. Xhaka, R. van Wolfswinkel, A. Kalulu, Albian Ajeti.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1574","checkdouble":"191896"},{"date":"10:15 24/07","title":"HLV Milan n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Bonucci c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sang M.U ho\u1eb7c Real?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/28/hlv-gattuso-muon-bonucci-o-lai-milan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, \"n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n\" trong pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p cho nhau.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Nan-nhan-cua-Sam-Ngoc-Duc-mong-muon-dieu-nay-sau-cu-dap-troi-gian-hinh-anh.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7\u00a0Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m</em>\u00a0<em>Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai CLB TP.HCM v\u00e0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/7 t\u1edbi, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn. Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, c\u00f2n Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p b\u00ean ph\u00eda Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. Song Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft ti\u1ebft ch\u1ebf c\u1ea3m x\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef 'n\u1ed3i c\u01a1m' cho nhau.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh chia s\u1ebb: \"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng qua r\u1ed3i n\u00ean t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i may m\u1eafn khi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb g\u00ec. Ch\u1ec9 mong Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c sau n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eebng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u00e1c \u00fd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u1eefa. \u0110\u00f4i ch\u00e2n gi\u00fap c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1m n\u00ean \u0111\u1eebng c\u1ed1 \u00fd tri\u1ec7t h\u1ea1 l\u1eabn nhau\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf sau pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CLB TP.HCM b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t 15 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-nhieu-lan-roi-291-191892.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-nhieu-lan-roi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/vleague/sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-nhieu-lan-roi-291-191892.html\">S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-168-191885.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/28/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-168-191885.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB TP.HCM Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1573","checkdouble":"191897"},{"date":"10:25 24/07","title":"Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/5/chelsea-chot-gia-ban-willian-cho-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua Willian nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Sau khi Antoine Griezmann \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/Chelsea-ban-Willian-cho-Barca-voi-gia-70-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua Willian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPhilippe Couttinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Barca mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-chuyen-nhuong/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea-187-191704.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua Willian</span>. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng song \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, sau \u0111\u00f3 Barca n\u00e2ng l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Barca g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, song Chelsea v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. Theo Daily Mail, HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Chelsea y\u00eau c\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103m nay s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 30, Barca s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian ghi ban\" title=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian ghi ban\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/barca-nang-gia-hoi-mua-willian-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo The Sun, Chelsea ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Willian cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu Willian. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Willian cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u1edf l\u1ea1i thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i, b\u1edfi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 The Blues y\u00eau c\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Barca ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb b\u1ecf m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1572","checkdouble":"191898"},{"date":"10:24 24/07","title":"\"Liverpool v\u1eabn c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/liverpool-van-con-thieu-mot-tien-dao-dang-cap-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Harry Kewell kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n chi ti\u00eau \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Liverpool chi ti\u00eau m\u1ea1nh tay</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n khi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh h\u1ea1ng n\u1eb7ng. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Naby Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson c\u0169ng m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp The Kop</span> v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e0 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ebf v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool Kewell khuy\u00ean The Kop mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool Kewell khuy\u00ean The Kop mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/liverpool-van-con-thieu-mot-tien-dao-dang-cap-the-gioi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool: Kewell khuy\u00ean Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n khi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean nh\u01b0 Mohamed Salah hay Virgil van Dijk \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u1ed1t trong v\u00f2ng 12 th\u00e1ng qua. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Harry Kewell cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Merseyside v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean t\u1edd Daily Express, Kewell cho hay: \u201c\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Man City qu\u00e1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt th\u00ec m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb lu m\u1edd. Nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Liverpool \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c. Ph\u00f2ng tr\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p m\u1ed9t trong ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u1eefa\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kewell k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o Liverpool m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0ng Kewell c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Liverpool. H\u1ecd v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Alexander-Arnold v\u00e0 Andrew Robertson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMane, Salah v\u00e0 Firmino \u0111\u1ec1u thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Henderson \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u mong mu\u1ed1n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n theo tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-don-tin-du-tu-hang-thu-matip-chan-thuong-172-191895.html\">Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Liverpool lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-danh-sach-7-cau-thu-giup-liverpool-thu-ve-100-trieu-bang-172-191890.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Danh s\u00e1ch 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap Liverpool thu v\u1ec1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1571","checkdouble":"191900"}]}